name: Dwimmered Magicite
desc: Activate this card by banishing 1 face-up monster you control or 1 monster in your GY; Special Summon this card as a Normal Monster (Spellcaster/LIGHT/ATK 0/DEF 0) with the same original Level as the banished monster's. (This card is also still a Trap.) You can only activate 1 "Dwimmered Magicite" per turn.
